"""
        Test that the equality/inequality operators return False/True when
        comparing two ModifyAttribute request payloads with different current
        attributes.
        """
a = payloads.ModifyAttributeRequestPayload(current_attribute=objects.
    CurrentAttribute(attribute=primitives.Enumeration(enums.
    CryptographicAlgorithm, enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, enums.Tags.
    CRYPTOGRAPHIC_ALGORITHM)))
b = payloads.ModifyAttributeRequestPayload(current_attribute=objects.
    CurrentAttribute(attribute=primitives.Integer(128, enums.Tags.
    CRYPTOGRAPHIC_LENGTH)))
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
